These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, mexican
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily
There 2 different types of food: plum, pepper
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Flower         | lily | marigold    |
| Food     | plum     | pepper      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, fisherman
City: hamburg, nizza
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the scientist##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Job      | fisherman  | scientist   |
| City   | nizza | hamburg  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, kale
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, nigerian
1. the person eating kale is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Food         | nectarine   | kale  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Nationality         | japanese   | nigerian |

