.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, sailing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, malaysian
1. the russian is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Sport          | tennis | sailing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| Nationality     | malaysian       | russian      |

