.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, singing
2 different games are played: go, monopoly
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, game
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | singing    |
| Game   | monopoly     | go      |
| Cigar         | bongani | game |

