.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, poker
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, february
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
3. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Game    | poker | scrabble     |
| Birthday     | february | may |
| Sport   | skiing | sailing    |

 #################################

 
